snippet.title: Playstation : Septentrion - Out of the Blue ~ Gameplay (JAP)
snippet.description:
Septentrion - Out of the Blue is an adventure by the Human Entertainment company that released back in 1999 exclusively for the Playstation and the Japanese market.

It's a 3D remake of the cult SNES game S.O.S.

For the intro :
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sH2Ysl7DQf4
